B.WP=s(["Pantastic is washing detergent comparable to Dawn dish soap.","It can be identified by its blue hue.","Pantastic is the basic chemical for jobs that require scrubbing, such as sinks, drains, and pulpers."],t.s)
B.agd=new A.ao("Pantastic",B.WP)
B.Rr=s(["Power Force is a premium cleaner/degreaser.","It can be identified by its red hue and mild citrus aroma.","Power Force is used to clean the floors because it is designed to help cut through heavy soil and grease."],t.s)
